task.summary: Adds expected file structure and populates the pom, cfg.xml and HibernateUtil files.
Adds enums for position type and result type as well as declarations for competition class.
Adds constructors and getters/setters to competition class.
Adds declarations, constructors and getter/setters for Team class.
Adds declarations, constructors and getter/setters for Employee parent class.
Adds declarations, constructors and getter/setters for Manager and Player child classes.
Adds class tests for getters to Competition and Team as well as get size functions and tests for teams/players and add team/player functions and tests.
Adds tests for setters for the Team class.
Adds tests for getters/setters for Employee/Manager/Player classes.
Adds annotations for all classes and refactors Employee/Manager/Player classes so that the child classes individually take the Team relationship.

Adds content to runner file and fixes issues with the previous setup of Many to One relationships with HashSets by having a new Team take in a competition and a new Player take in a team upon construction.
Adds tests and methods for Team class to increment games played/won/drawn/lost, increase goals scored/conceded and increase points for win/draw.
Adds tests and methods for updateWinProportion for the Manager class and increment Goals/Assists for the player class.
Adds a DBHelper method for updating team/manager stats after a game.
Updates addTeamToCompetition and addPlayerToTeam methods to take account of the capacities in each respectively.
Adds DBHelperTest to test all DBHelper methods.
Adds DBHelper method and test for returning list of teams ordered by points. Also refactors DBHelperTest for delete by calling the assertions in the @After method.
Adds a bug fix to stop the team class eagerly bringing back it's players teams when using getAll to bring back a list of all teams.
